        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Many People Choose Side Stone Rings for a Classic Look",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Many People Choose Side Stone Rings for a Classic Look</h2>",
            "custom_id": "why-many",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_FbghAK": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Side stone rings have been popular for years because they feel timeless. They add brilliance without changing the shape of the center diamond.</p><p>Many buyers like how the smaller stones gradually lead the eye toward the center diamond.</p><p>Designs like the Distinctive<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-round\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Round Solitaire\"> Round Solitaire</a> Accent Ring or the Oval Cut with Side Diamonds Accent Engagement Ring reflect this approach. The diamonds along the band enhance the ring without competing with the center stone.</p><p>This style works especially well for people who want something elegant but not overly flashy.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Halo Rings Are Often Chosen for Maximum Sparkle",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Halo Rings Are Often Chosen for Maximum Sparkle</h2>",
            "custom_id": "why-halo",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_p8RgGz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Halo rings appeal to people who want their diamond ring to have a stronger presence.</p><p>Because the center diamond is surrounded by smaller stones, the ring appears brighter and sometimes even larger.</p><p>Halo settings are also very versatile. They can work with round, oval, cushion, and marquise diamonds.</p><p>For instance, Lucira’s <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings-marquise\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Marquise Cut Engagement Ring\">Marquise Cut Engagement Ring</a> with Halo Setting shows how the halo highlights the unique shape of the marquise diamond while adding extra brilliance.</p><p>Many engagement ring buyers choose halo settings when they want a ring that feels luxurious and eye-catching.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
